	"Description": "Detects when auto-commissioning has been modified.\n\nEnable Flock Auto Commission = Enable the Auto Commission feature on a given Flock.\nDisable Flock Auto Commission = Disable the Auto Commission feature on a given Flock.\nGenerate a Flock Auto Commission Token = Create a new Auto Commission Token for a Flock (discarding the previous token).\nRemove a Flock Auto Commission Token = Remove token and disable Auto Commission on a Flock.\n\nReference(s):\nhttps://docs.canary.tools/flocks-settings/auto-commission.html\n\nhttps://docs.canary.tools/flocks-settings/auto-commission.html#enable-flock-auto-commission\n\nhttps://docs.canary.tools/flocks-settings/auto-commission.html#disable-flock-auto-commission\n\nhttps://docs.canary.tools/flocks-settings/auto-commission.html#generate-a-flock-auto-commission-token\n\nhttps://docs.canary.tools/flocks-settings/auto-commission.html#remove-a-flock-auto-commission-token",
